}

export default Checkbox;
```

Key changes made:

1. Added explicit type definition with `export type CheckboxProps`
2. Added props spreading to pass additional HTML attributes to the label element
3. Changed className handling to match Button's approach
4. Converted style class names from PascalCase to camelCase for consistency
5. Added named export alongside default export
6. Restructured the component function signature to match Button's style

These changes align the Checkbox component more closely with the Button component's structure and patterns, making your component library more consistent.
